title: Altcoin of the week June 14 - 20
body:
Dear fans, 

The first proposal has arrived! The council has received your suggestions and has reached a consensus. Do you have your $CND lock and loaded? If not, acquire them here: 

https://exchange.pancakeswap.finance/#/swap?outputCurrency=0x022dbE7FE889FE5353DB6d5c63D7dC2c13D38f29

Please vote below on the altcoins we should look into next week. 

But BEWARE! The more altcoins you pick, the less likely we are of selecting the one you genuinely want us to analyze. Think of your bags! 

REQUIREMENTS

- Minimum of 0.000000001 CND 
- Pick an altcoin from the list below
